data.description: Prime waterfront with swimming pool in Inverness, located on Lake Spivey and connecting  to  the Chain of Lakes. The SUNSET ends here view some of the most amazing sunsets!  This home is at the end of a cul-de-sac and  allowa for a most unusual  setting for you and your family and boat. 3 bedroom and 2 baths, 2 car garage. Home has a very large florida room  with split unit to cool or heat.   New Roof in 2023, new windows, 2023, newer Central Air, Electrical panel was replaced in 2019,   Yard is completely fenced,  Boat Dock, This home has it all and is ready for you to make it your home.  pool was redone in 2022,  Must see the beautiful lake home.  schedule your appt today
